Interest on the debt evidenced by this note shall not exceed the maximum amount of
non-usurious interest that may be contracted for, taken, reserved, charged or received under
law; any interest in excess of that maximum amount shall be credited on the principal of the
debt or if that has been unpaid, refunded. On any acceleration or required or permitted
prepayment, any such excess shall be canceled automatically as of the acceleration or
prepayment or, if already paid, credited on the principal of the debt, or if the principal of the debt
has been paid, refunded. This provision overrides other provision in this and all other
instruments Concerning the debt.
Each Maker is responsible for all represented by this note.
When the context requires, singular nouns and pronouns include the plural.
Hector Rodriguez
Suhail Rodwy Dasie
Suhail Rodriguez
Date: 07-28 -2022
Date: 01-28-2002
Sworn and subscribed before me on this date_23 day of Tatua24 2022
Notary Public in and for Bexar County, Texas
LUCIA O ESTRADA
MY COMMISSION EXPIRES
